cu.explanation_en: Setting the GNB IPv4 address for NGU to an invalid format with octet >255 will cause IP parsing errors and prevent NGU connection establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting the local N port D to 0 causes port binding failures and disrupts F1 interface communication.
du.explanation_zh: 將本地 N 端口 D 設定為 0 會導致端口綁定失敗，並干擾 F1 接口通信。
